Package: eventb-to-txt
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: convert Event-B machines and contexts to CamilleX text
 eventb-to-txt converts Event-B machines and contexts (.bum/.buc files or zip
 archives exported from Rodin) into plain-text CamilleX notation.
 .
 It reads models produced by Rodin 3.0 and later and needs no Rodin
 installation, making it convenient for diffing models, code review and
 lightweight inspection of Event-B developments.
